And he even took the receipt of the box (maybe so I couldn't see what time was on it)? Totally unacceptable. It was 30 min late, cold,  missing the onions (dixie chicken) and I was lied to about how fresh it was.  Extremely unhappy about this experience. The  time before was almost as bad.  Not as late,  and not cold,  not far from it.  If you can't get the pizza made,  and delivered hot in the time frame you give me,  then you should remake it or possibly not make until you know it will arrive hot! I won't be ordering from again.
